      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\nあっ、あそこにいるのが例の犯人ですね！？",
      "startTime": 3.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "通報にあった通り、お腹にダイナマイトを巻いてますね\nもし、こんな所であれが爆発したら……！",
      "startTime": 12.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.5333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。……警察も、あの爆発物のせいで\n遠巻きに包囲するしか、まだ出来ていないみたいだな",
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-mobmen001.m4a",
      "text": "おらー！！　このダイナマイトが目に入らねぇのか！！\n金だ、今すぐ金を持って来ーい！！",
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2666653951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "大変です！　爆発なんか起きたら\n農家さんが育てたお米も、全部ダメになっちゃいます！",
      "startTime": 34.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.3333317757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-mobmen002.m4a",
      "text": "おらはもう、山形なんてド田舎は嫌だー！！\n金を持って、おらは東京さ行くだー！！",
      "startTime": 42.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-mobmen003.m4a",
      "text": "東京で、電車が五分に一本来るとこ住むんだ\nTV番組も周回遅れの田舎なんて、もう嫌だあああ！",
      "startTime": 50.2333320617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.5666615486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（あの犯人役の人、凄い熱演だなぁ）\n（大分、本音も混じってそうな叫びだけど……）",
      "startTime": 60.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2333320617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことのために、お米とみんなを危険に晒すなんて\n許せません、絶対に逮捕します！！",
      "startTime": 67.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（いけない、すみれはドッキリを信じ切ってるんだから）\n（俺もちゃんと、それに合わせないと）",
      "startTime": 73.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.345826600003,
          "startTime": 74.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7333353679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、カメラさん、マイクさん\n警察の規制線より内側に入ったらダメですよ",
      "startTime": 77.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "万が一、爆発に巻き込まれてはいけませんから\n{user}さん達は後ろに下がってて下さい",
      "startTime": 84.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7999900501
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、すみれを置いて俺だけ避難する訳には……",
      "startTime": 87.7999900501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3000071209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "私は、ここでみんなを守ります\nだって今日は、私が警察署長なんですから！",
      "startTime": 94.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7346.006139400004,
          "startTime": 101.7793394727
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（すみれ、なんて立派な志なんだ……！）",
      "startTime": 98.1333305043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4333355905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　私が犯人を説得するんですか？",
      "startTime": 103.4333355905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7000050862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのは、専門の交渉担当の人がやるものじゃ……\nえ、山形県警のネゴシエーターはすぐには来られない？",
      "startTime": 112.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "意外と警察に詳しいんだな、すみれ",
      "startTime": 117.6000022572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5333348592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "子供の頃、刑事物のドラマに出たことがあって\nその時、ネゴシエーター役の人もいたんです",
      "startTime": 124.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.5333287557
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、専門の方が来られないのは……わ、分かりました\n署長として、見事、犯人を説得してみせます！！",
      "startTime": 135.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "犯人に告ぐー！！\nあなたは包囲されています、大人しく投降しなさーい！",
      "startTime": 143.3333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.3333292644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-mobmen004.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こっちに来るんじゃねぇ！！\nこれ以上おらに近づいたら、こいつに火を点けるぞ！？",
      "startTime": 151.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.0000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "東京にばっかり、目を向けなくたって\n山形にもいいところが沢山ありますよー！！",
      "startTime": 158.6666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "山形には温泉もわいてますし、スキーも滑り放題ですし\nご近所から野菜もお裾分けしてもらえますし！",
      "startTime": 167.3000132244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.0999949138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "東京に行ったら、芋煮もあんまり食べられませんよー！\n「それ豚汁じゃないの？」とか言われちゃいますよー！",
      "startTime": 175.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.333308125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-mobmen005.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、うるせえ！　山形と東京を行き来してるやつに\nおらの気持ちなんか、分かるもんかぁー！！",
      "startTime": 184.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "うっ。あの犯人の方、私のことをよくご存じですね……\nえっと、えっと、どうしよう",
      "startTime": 194.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.3999949138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "そ……そこで、あなたが田んぼと一緒に爆発したら\nご家族のみなさんも悲しみますよー！！",
      "startTime": 202.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "犯人役の男性",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_02-mobmen006.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、うるせえ！\n母ちゃんは、おらの母ちゃんは関係ねぇだろ！？",
      "startTime": 207.3333353678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ricefield-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ricefield-00-noon",
